    "body": "See: https://github.com/spack/spack/issues/8232\r\n\r\nThis updates Spack to apply environment modifications after loading modules: those associated with external packages, as well as those associated with compilers. This means that:\r\n\r\n* Spack settings for `CC` take precedence over modules setting `CC`\r\n* Spack `prepend_path` actions take precedence over environment variable path modifications from modules\r\n\r\nBefore this PR both of these were not necessarily true.",
